    "602411": [
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Columbina Hyposelenia. That's a wonderful name."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "I never thought that \"Columbina\" would become my real name."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "But after I met you, and my other friends, the things that this name stood for slowly began to change."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "It went being from a Fatui codename... to \"something my friends call me.\""
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "(How much she's changed since we first met... She never used to share her innermost thoughts.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Hmm? What is it? Why aren't you saying anything?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "I'm just so happy for you."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Hehe, thank you. So, where's everyone else?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "We can go and meet them very soon. Everyone went to different places to try calling your name."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Great. I'd like to thank them as well. Everyone's done so much for me — searching for my name, entering those ancient ruins..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Huh? Wait, so you were..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Yes, I was there. Not physically, but my consciousness was still holding on. I followed you the whole way."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "...Starting from when?"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "You turned around and called out my name while you were in Nasha Town. Do you remember?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "(Ah, so that's what that was...)"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "(I could've sworn I felt someone pat me on the back... And deep down, I think I knew that it was Columbina.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Let's go. We don't want to keep them waiting."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Sure. In that case, come with me."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Ah, but..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Hmm?"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Before that... Could you call my name one more time?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Haha..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Sure. Come with me, Columbina Hyposelenia."
        }
    ],
    "602412": [
        {
            "N": "",
            "T": "Columbina spreads the good news to your friends by way of small animals and kuuhenki..."
        },
        {
            "N": "",
            "T": "But since not everyone speaks critter sign language, some friends took longer than others to get the message."
        },
        {
            "N": "Lauma",
            "T": "...! Columbina! Oh, this truly is wonderful..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "...! L—Lauma... I can't... breathe..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Varka",
            "T": "Haha, just in time for Moon-Prayer Night! It's good to have you back, Miss Columbina."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Yeah! We were worried sick!"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Thank you, my friends. With your help, I now have a name that belongs to me."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nefer",
            "T": "Columbina Hyposelenia... Where's the second half from? You added it yourself?"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "That's right, it means..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Lauma",
            "T": "Born beneath the moon."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "Yes, and by extension, it can also mean \"born beneath this world.\""
        },
        {
            "N": "The Knave",
            "T": "A fine name."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "Ahem! Now, as much as it pains me to interrupt this beautiful reunion, I feel obliged to remind you that... the Moon-Prayer Night celebrations in Nasha Town have already begun!"
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "Don't you want to enjoy the festivities? There's so much to see and do! ...And some of the ambient lighting and entertainments were sponsored by the kind souls in the Hexenzirkel!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Nicole? Uh... Why've you turned into a Dodoco?"
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "So you're Ms. Nicole... Thank you for helping us, and for helping me find my name. It's nice to finally hear your voice."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "You're quite welcome. Guiding lost people to hidden treasure is what we Seelie do."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "And if you ask me, spiritual treasures are far more precious than material ones! Chests are all well and good, but this? This was what it's all about! Ah, so satisfying!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Uhhh..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "Hehe. Anyway, I had to go help Alice — it seems like she ran into some trouble. That's why I couldn't be here in person."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "But don't worry! We're with you in spirit! We'll be celebrating right along with you."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nicole",
            "T": "Keep an eye out for the Hexenzirkel's festive stalls in Nasha Town! I think you'll like what we came up with. Alice said she even managed to rope \"B\" in this time."
        },
        {
            "N": "Lauma",
            "T": "The Frostmoon Scions have also prepared various attractions. I believe Aino, Ineffa, and their crew are setting things up as we speak."
        },
        {
            "N": "Lauma",
            "T": "On that note... Nefer, about that request I made..."
        },
        {
            "N": "Nefer",
            "T": "It's all in hand. Jahoda is on site to ensure that everything goes off without a hitch."
        },
        {
            "N": "Lauma",
            "T": "#Wonderful. In that case... {NICKNAME}?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Got it."
        },
        {
            "N": "Columbina",
            "T": "...Huh?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Come on, Columbina. It's time to celebrate the best Moon-Prayer Night ever."
        }
    ],
