    "602703": [
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "#{NICKNAME}."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Hey there, Columbina! Are you done checking out the festive amusements already?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Are you sure you don't wanna look around some more? You might not get another opportunity like this for a while..."
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "..."
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "(Right now, what I'd like to do is...)"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "(...Actually, I'd like to have a bit more fun.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "You're right... I'm not ready for this night to end just yet."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Yeah, that's the spirit! Take your time, Columbina. The most important thing is to have no regrets!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "We'll be right here if you need us!"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Okay, thank you."
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "(...I think I've had my fill.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Thank you. But I think I've had enough fun for one night."
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "I've made plenty of precious memories."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "...Really? You're sure you don't wanna have a little more fun out there? Final answer?"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "(Final answer.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Yes, I am sure."
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "(Reconsider.)"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Hmm... Maybe I should think about this more carefully..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Would you like some Moon-Prayer Candy?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Ooh, candy for us? Thanks a bunch, Columbina! Don't mind if we do!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Whoa, this one's intense! Mmm, but it's sooo tasty!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "#What about you, {NICKNAME}? How does yours taste?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Like Smetana, I think... A very novel flavor."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Sounds good! Paimon's drooling now... Are there any more Smetana candies in the box?"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Yes, I believe so."
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Kay, gotcha. Let's see..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Have you tried any of them yourself?"
        },
        {
            "N": "The Damselette",
            "T": "Ah..."
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "Paimon, could you pick out three Smetana-flavored candies?"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Sure!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "This one, and... Yep, this one looks right, too... Okay, that's three!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_1005",
            "T": "Here we go. One per person!"
        },
        {
            "N": "_0",
            "T": "All together, then?"
        },
        {
            "N": "All Three Together",
            "T": "It's so sweet!"
        }
    ],
